=== Expected Behavior Analysis ===
Input values: -16 to -1 (all negative)

For MAX-POOL (padding should be -infinity):
  pooled[0,0] = -11 (max of 4 valid cells with -inf padding elsewhere)
  pooled[1,1] = -6 (max of 9-cell window fully inside input)
