For CONV/SUM (padding should be 0):
  conv[0,0] = sum of 4 values (corner) = -16-15-12-11 = -54
  conv[1,1] = sum of 9 values (center) = -16-15-14-12-11-10-8-7-6 = -99

If conv shows -inf at edges, the padding reset failed.

